Service Overview: The Digital Product factory is a prototype Accelerator. It equips organizations with rapid, customizable digital product prototypes that deliver University Services. Designed to advance from concept to prototype in just 10 minutes, our service streamlines the development process, enabling universities to focus exclusively on refinement and deployment.


Product Offerings:

  General Department Services:

  • Flexible non-IT Customer Support Services for faculty, staff, students and university affiliates 
  • Workflows streamline tasks and offer end-to-end visibility
  • Training, knowledge, and checklists help to improve the end-to-end experience for individuals involved.

 Key Advantages:

  1. Fast Time to Value: From initiation to prototype in 15 minutes.
  2. Configurability: Flexible solutions adaptable to specific agency needs.
  3. Integration Ready: Designed for easy integration with existing services.
  4. Secure and Compliant: Meets stringent government security and compliance standards.
